            <abstract id="ref44" label="Abstract">This collection documents the efforts of the grass-roots organization known as The Drive to Protect the Ladies' Mile to designate this area in Manhattan as a historic district. It includes letters of support, research, submissions to the Landmarks Commission, and related materials.</abstract>
